{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847008132,"sessionID":"ses_28745fd73ffepLMcTLtooTm4f5","part":{"id":"prt_d78bae772001mppMhPGJW8ZTRp","messageID":"msg_d78bad7c7001TjbvFjaz5fryx6","sessionID":"ses_28745fd73ffepLMcTLtooTm4f5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7bb223c5ce5149a5b023da77b1678096","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md","limit":100,"offset":700},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n700:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n701:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n702:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n703:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n704:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n705:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n706:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n707:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n708:     AgentRuntimeExpansion\n709: }\n710: ```\n711: \n712: **CodeInterpreterInterface** (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`)\n713: \n714: ```go\n715: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n716:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n717:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n718:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n719:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n720:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n721:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n722:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n723:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n724:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n725:     CodeInterpreterExpansion\n726: }\n727: ```\n728: \n729: ## Error Handling\n730: \n731: ### Validation Errors\n732: \n733: CRD validation errors are enforced by Kubernetes API server:\n734: \n735: 1. **Missing required fields**: `spec.maxSessionDuration`, `spec.sessionTimeout`, `spec.targetPort` (AgentRuntime)\n736: 2. **Invalid enum values**: `protocol` must be `HTTP` or `HTTPS`\n737: 3. **Port range violations**: `port` must be between 1 and 65535\n738: 4. **Array minimum**: `targetPort` must have at least one element\n739: \n740: ### Client-Go Error Handling\n741: \n742: ```go\n743: // Common error patterns\n744: err := client.AgentRuntimes(namespace).Create(ctx, &agentRuntime, opts)\n745: if errors.IsAlreadyExists(err) {\n746:     // Handle conflict\n747: } else if errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n748:     // Handle not found\n749: } else if errors.IsInvalid(err) {\n750:     // Handle validation error\n751: } else if errors.IsForbidden(err) {\n752:     // Handle RBAC error\n753: } else if err != nil {\n754:     // Handle other errors\n755: }\n756: ```\n757: \n758: ### Informer Error Handling\n759: \n760: ```go\n761: informer.AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n762:     AddFunc: func(obj interface{}) {\n763:         if runtimeObj, ok := obj.(metav1.Object); ok {\n764:             klog.Infof(\"AgentRuntime %s added\", runtimeObj.GetName())\n765:         }\n766:     },\n767:     UpdateFunc: func(oldObj, newObj interface{}) {\n768:         oldRuntime := oldObj.(*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n769:         newRuntime := newObj.(*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n770:         if oldRuntime.Generation != newRuntime.Generation {\n771:             klog.Infof(\"AgentRuntime %s generation changed\", newRuntime.Name)\n772:         }\n773:     },\n774:     DeleteFunc: func(obj interface{}) {\n775:         if runtimeObj, ok := obj.(metav1.Object); ok {\n776:             klog.Infof(\"AgentRuntime %s deleted\", runtimeObj.GetName())\n777:         }\n778:     },\n779: })\n780: ```\n781: \n782: ## Testing Strategy\n783: \n784: ### Unit Tests\n785: \n786: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types_test.go`\n787: \n788: ```go\n789: package v1alpha1_test\n790: \n791: import (\n792:     . \"github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2\"\n793:     . \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n794:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n795:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n796: )\n797: \n798: var _ = Describe(\"AgentRuntime\", func() {\n799:     Describe(\"Spec defaults\", func() {\n\n(Showing lines 700-799 of 1241. Use offset=800 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeExpansion\n}\n```\n\n**CodeInterpreterInterface** (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`)\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md","time":{"start":1775847008122,"end":1775847008131}}}}
